verbose_text: Similarly to CLU, alpha 2 M significantly inhibited the aggregation of alphaS under these conditions (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), and again, after 6 hr of incubation, the resulting small alphaS oligomers showed a broad distribution centered around an equimolar stoichiometry with alpha 2 M (XREF_FIG A and 2C).
evidence: alpha 2 M significantly inhibited the aggregation of alphaS
